channel.description:
I was watching Futurama just now and seem this image below: You guys think you're smart and cartoons are stupid, check this out, this one scene from Futurama has more knowledge in it then you probably ever thought as deep as you could think.
(P.S. Artists really have a lot of power and they use art to teach other people.)
